1.2.name: wordpress/adsense-click-fraud-monitoring
1.2.description:
This Google AdSense Plugin blocks visitor from seeing your ads when they click multiple times on them.
- Prevents to be banned and excluded from your AdSense account due to malicious or unintended third party clicks on advertisements on your website.
